OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777889102
OL,3,C5G mast set on fire in Oxford
OL,5,FThe investigating officer, Detective
OL,6,FConstable Francesca Maurice-Williams,
OL,7,Fsaid: "I am appealing for witnesses to
OL,8,Fthis incident that we believe is Arson.
OL,10,F"I would ask that anyone who was in or
OL,11,Fnear to the area to please get in
OL,12,Ftouch with us if you saw anything or
OL,13,Fhave any information.
OL,15,F"If you have any information, you can
OL,16,Fcontact police by calling the 24-hour
OL,17,Fnon-emergency number 101, quoting
OL,18,Freference number 43260210718, or by
OL,19,Fmaking a report online."
