OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777889102
OL,3,C5G mast set on fire in Oxford
OL,5,FThis is the second time in less than
OL,6,Ftwo months that a 5G mast has been set
OL,7,Fon fire in Oxford after a previous
OL,8,Fincident brought major disruption to
OL,9,Fthe A40.
OL,11,FAt around 8.45pm on March 5, one or
OL,12,Fmore people broke into a compartment
OL,13,Fof a 5G mast near Cutteslowe
OL,14,FRoundabout.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/3
